cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the associated paper and this repository."
title: "pico2w-microros-benchmark"
abstract: >
  Reproducibility repository for the IEEE conference paper
  'Effectiveness of micro-ROS over WiFi'. Contains the data, runner scripts,
  firmware overlays, and analysis tools used to benchmark micro-ROS
  communication performance on the Raspberry Pi Pico 2W across serial and
  WiFi transports at 1, 10, and 100 Hz.
type: software
authors:
